\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {113}{\ignorespaces The same eight length-3 paths plotted as random walks \(X_n\) (left) and as stock paths \(S_n = 4 \cdot 2^{X_n}\) on a log axis (right). The two pictures are the same plot in different coordinates: \(\log _2(S_n/4) = X_n\).}}{238}{figure.0.113}\protected@file@percent }
